('p0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000035', 'c0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000004', 'b0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000009', 'Under Armour Storm Fleece Hoodie', 'under-armour-storm-hoodie', 'Water-resistant, thermal fleece training hooded pullover.', 'Incorporates UA Storm technology that repels heavy mist without losing breathability. Extremely soft interior insulating heat.', 'UA-STRM-HDD', 72000.00, 65000.00, 9.72, 4.59, 214, 90, '[{"name": "Size", "values": ["S", "M", "L", "XL", "XXL"]}, {"name": "Color", "values": ["Charcoal Grey", "Pitch Black"]}]'::jsonb, 'active'),
